OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLow cloud in the west will
OL,6,Fgradually become confined to coasts
OL,7,Fduring the day, allowing very warm
OL,8,Fsunshine to develop elsewhere. The
OL,9,Fbest of the sunshine likely in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FVery
OL,13,Fwarm over the Bank Holiday weekend
OL,14,Fwith plenty of sunshine and light
OL,15,Fwinds. Any early morning cloud should
OL,16,Fburn back to the coasts through the
OL,17,Fmorning each day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
